{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775872073839,"sessionID":"ses_285c6eb7bffesHDqSBGmAxReej","part":{"id":"prt_d7a3948e8001z2LKMJbjbT8nVZ","messageID":"msg_d7a393afb001htqHlJh35Bi4lM","sessionID":"ses_285c6eb7bffesHDqSBGmAxReej","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-015: PicoD е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢ API - Task List\n2: \n3: ## Phase 1: API Design and Types\n4: \n5: - [ ] **T-001**: Define ExecutionRequest and ExecutionResult types\n6:   - Status: pending\n7:   - Estimated: 2h\n8: \n9: - [ ] **T-002**: Define ExecutionStatus and ExecutionState enums\n10:   - Status: pending\n11:   - Estimated: 1h\n12: \n13: - [ ] **T-003**: Define ResourceConstraints struct\n14:   - Status: pending\n15:   - Estimated: 1h\n16: \n17: - [ ] **T-004**: Define ExecutionError type and error codes\n18:   - Status: pending\n19:   - Estimated: 1h\n20: \n21: ## Phase 2: Core Executor Implementation\n22: \n23: - [ ] **T-005**: Create CommandExecutor struct with dependencies\n24:   - Status: pending\n25:   - Estimated: 2h\n26: \n27: - [ ] **T-006**: Implement Execute (synchronous) method\n28:   - Status: pending\n29:   - Estimated: 4h\n30: \n31: - [ ] **T-007**: Implement ExecuteAsync method\n32:   - Status: pending\n33:   - Estimated: 3h\n34: \n35: - [ ] **T-008**: Implement GetStatus method\n36:   - Status: pending\n37:   - Estimated: 2h\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T-009**: Implement Cancel method\n40:   - Status: pending\n41:   - Estimated: 2h\n42: \n43: ## Phase 3: Output Handling\n44: \n45: - [ ] **T-010**: Implement output capture mechanism\n46:   - Status: pending\n47:   - Estimated: 3h\n48: \n49: - [ ] **T-011**: Implement StreamOutput method\n50:   - Status: pending\n51:   - Estimated: 4h\n52: \n53: - [ ] **T-012**: Add output buffering and size limits\n54:   - Status: pending\n55:   - Estimated: 2h\n56: \n57: ## Phase 4: Status Management\n58: \n59: - [ ] **T-013**: Implement execution status lifecycle\n60:   - Status: pending\n61:   - Estimated: 3h\n62: \n63: - [ ] **T-014**: Integrate with status store for persistence\n64:   - Status: pending\n65:   - Estimated: 2h\n66: \n67: - [ ] **T-015**: Add timeout enforcement\n68:   - Status: pending\n69:   - Estimated: 2h\n70: \n71: ## Phase 5: Testing\n72: \n73: - [ ] **T-016**: Create mock sandbox client\n74:   - Status: pending\n75:   - Estimated: 2h\n76: \n77: - [ ] **T-017**: Write unit tests for Execute\n78:   - Status: pending\n79:   - Estimated: 4h\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T-018**: Write unit tests for async operations\n82:   - Status: pending\n83:   - Estimated: 3h\n84: \n85: - [ ] **T-019**: Write unit tests for status and cancel\n86:   - Status: pending\n87:   - Estimated: 3h\n88: \n89: - [ ] **T-020**: Write integration tests\n90:   - Status: pending\n91:   - Estimated: 4h\n92: \n93: ## Summary\n94: \n95: - Total tasks: 20\n96: - Pending: 20\n97: - In Progress: 0\n98: - Completed: 0\n99: - Total estimated: ~41 hours (5 days)\n\n(End of file - total 99 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015: PicoD е‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢ API - Task List\n\n## Phase 1: API Design and Types\n\n- [ ] **T-001**: Define ExecutionRequest and ExecutionResult types\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 2h\n\n- [ ] **T-002**: Define ExecutionStatus and ExecutionState enums\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 1h\n\n- [ ] **T-003**: Define ResourceConstraints struct\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 1h\n\n- [ ] **T-004**: Define ExecutionError type and error codes\n  - Status: pending\n  - Estimated: 1h\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775872073