 Write `TestStreamOutput_StdoutStderrSeparated` | Type field correct per stream | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** StreamOutput tests pass.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.19 вҖ” Unit Tests вҖ” Error Types\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.19.1 | Write `TestErrors_AllDefined` | All 13 errors are non-nil | 0.5h |\n| 4.19.2 | Write `TestErrors_Messages` | Error messages match spec | 0.5h |\n| 4.19.3 | Write `TestExecutionError_Struct` | Code, Message, Details accessible | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Error tests pass.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.20 вҖ” Integration Tests\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.20.1 | Create `pkg/picod/executor_integration_test.go` | File created with build tag | 0.5h |\n| 4.20.2 | Write `TestIntegration_EndToEndSync` | Full sync execution flow | 1h |\n| 4.20.3 | Write `TestIntegration_EndToEndAsync` | Full async execution flow | 1h |\n| 4.20.4 | Write `TestIntegration_ConcurrentExecutions` | 10 parallel executions | 1h |\n| 4.20.5 | Write `TestIntegration_Cancellation` | Cancel running execution | 1h |\n| 4.20.6 | Write `TestIntegration_OutputStreaming` | Stream output from async execution | 1h |\n| 4.20.7 | Write `TestIntegration_ResourceLimits` | Memory/CPU limits enforced | 1h |\n| 4.20.8 | Write `TestIntegration_StatusPersistence` | Status survives executor restart | 1h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Integration tests pass with real sandbox (AR-009) and store (AR-012+).\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.21 вҖ” Mock Implementations\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.21.1 | Create `pkg/picod/mock_sandbox.go` with `MockSandboxClient` | Implements SandboxClient interface | 1h |\n| 4.21.2 | Create `pkg/picod/mock_store.go` with `MockExecutionStore` | Implements store operations | 1h |\n| 4.21.3 | Add mock control methods (SetResponse, SetError, etc.) | Mocks configurable | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Mocks work for unit testing without real dependencies.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.22 вҖ” Documentation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.22.1 | Add package-level GoDoc for `pkg/picod` | `go doc ./pkg/picod` shows overview | 0.5h |\n| 4.22.2 | Document all exported types with GoDoc | Clear purpose documented | 0.5h |\n| 4.22.3 | Document all exported methods with GoDoc | Parameters and return values documented | 0.5h |\n| 4.22.4 | Add execution flow documentation | PendingвҶ’RunningвҶ’Completed diagram | 0.5h |\n| 4.22.5 | Document environment variables | PICOD_* variables listed | 0.5h |\n| 4.22.6 | Add usage examples in code comments | Example code in godoc | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Code is well-documented for future maintainers.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| ST-4.1: Type Definitions | 10 | 5h |\n| ST-4.2: Error Definitions | 13 | 3h |\n| ST-4.3: Request Validation | 8 | 4h |\n| ST-4.4: Executor Structure | 7 | 4h |\n| ST-4.5: Sync Execution | 11 | 6h |\n| ST-4.6: Async Execution | 7 | 3.5h |\n| ST-4.7: Status Management | 9 | 4.5h |\n| ST-4.8: Cancellation | 6 | 3h |\n| ST-4.9: Output Streaming | 10 | 5h |\n| ST-4.10: Sandbox Integration | 8 | 4h |\n| ST-4.11: Store Integration | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.12: Unit Tests (Types) | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.13: Unit Tests (Validation) | 7 | 3.5h |\n| ST-4.14: Unit Tests (Execute) | 8 | 4h |\n| ST-4.15: Unit Tests (ExecuteAsync) | 5 | 3h |\n| ST-4.16: Unit Tests (GetStatus) | 6 | 3h |\n| ST-4.17: Unit Tests (Cancel) | 5 | 2.5h |\n| ST-4.18: Unit Tests (StreamOutput) | 5 | 3h |\n| ST-4.19: Unit Tests (Errors) | 3 | 1.5h |\n| ST-4.20: Integration Tests | 8 | 7h |\n| ST-4.21: Mock Implementations | 3 | 2.5h |\n| ST-4.22: Documentation | 6 | 3h |\n| **Total** | **153** | **73h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/types.go` вҖ” Type definitions\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/errors.go` вҖ” Error type definitions\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/validation.go` вҖ” Request validation\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/executor.go` вҖ” CommandExecutor implementation\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/output.go` вҖ” Output capture and streaming\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/sandbox_client.go` вҖ” Sandbox integration\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/status.go` вҖ” Status management\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/executor_test.go` вҖ” Unit tests\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/executor_integration_test.go` вҖ” Integration tests\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/mock_sandbox.go` вҖ” Mock sandbox client\n- [ ] `pkg/picod/mock_store.go` вҖ” Mock store\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build verification\ngo build ./pkg/picod/...\n\n# Unit test verification (all picod tests)\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -v\n\n# Specific test suites\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestExecute -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestExecuteAsync -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestGetStatus -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestCancel -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestStreamOutput -v\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -run TestValidation -v\n\n# Race detection\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -race\n\n# Coverage report\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -cover\n\n# Integration tests (requires Docker/sandbox)\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -tags=integration -v\n```\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 153 tasks complete\n- [ ] `CommandExecutor` interface fully implemented\n- [ ] All validation rules implemented with tests\n- [ ] Unit tests pass (>85% coverage for core files)\n- [ ] Integration tests pass with real sandbox and store\n- [ ] Race detector clean\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/picod/...` succeeds\n- [ ] Documentation complete with GoDoc\n- [ ] Mock implementations provided for unit testing\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|\n| AR-009: Sandbox Interface | Command execution in sandboxes |\n| AR-012: Store Interface | Status persistence |\n| AR-013: Redis Implementation | Store backend option |\n| AR-014: Valkey Implementation | Store backend option |\n| `github.com/google/uuid` | ExecutionID generation |\n| `pkg/common/types` | Shared types |\n\n---\n\n## Design Notes\n\n- **Execution ID format:** `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+`, 8-64 characters\n- **State machine:** pending вҶ’ running вҶ’ completed | failed | cancelled\n- **Terminal states:** completed, failed, cancelled (immutable)\n- **Output buffering:** Circular buffer with configurable size\n- **Concurrency:** Semaphore-based limit enforcement\n- **Timeout:** Context-based with cancellation propagation\n- **Sandbox integration:** Via AR-009 interface\n- **Store integration:** Via AR-012 interface\n- **Environment config:** PICOD_* variables\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775872320454,"end":1775872320492}}}}
